plyTime":"2020-11-02T08:35:57.000Z","msg":"我入到嚟"},{"pid":"06409f893335d728f252cb1ada0edbb966778786","tid":2267604,"uid":129169,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:38:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MbgD8Hm.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMbgD8Hm.gif&h=cb5be47c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"801ebdcad6769a534188d60674b865f1df9c8ae3","tid":2267604,"uid":45353,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:39:46.000Z","msg":"唔係心有愧邊會咁大反應<br />\n<br />\n自己都面對唔到自己"},{"pid":"c20bb15cb256605c0c5157a07413607090af27f2","tid":2267604,"uid":174767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:41:29.000Z","msg":"當年個陣老泥妹味正到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baba4f67256852302a44fa3ec96a0c913ece941e","tid":2267604,"uid":307712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:43:13.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"77d12b63a913b7ba83ac1d46d347145893f79f9a","tid":2267604,"uid":178332,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:46:45.000Z","msg":"啫係我係你阿媽我就可以隨便打你嘅意思<br />\n無論你做乜我都要尊重你？<br />\n同小朋友相處 尊重唔係單方面 係要互相 唔係唔好怪佢地大個咗唔親你⋯⋯<br />\n畀父母打塊面真係會記一世<br />\n對仔喺學校已經畀人笑到面都黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有病就好心睇醫生啦<br />\n雖然佢當年重係minor都係受害者<br />\n但而家唔係喇掛 唔學下點處理 下下靠打 重要公開講自己打仔好似好威咁<br />\n我驚佢遲早畀對仔一齊殺死佢"},{"pid":"8a1657fd86a4e714e0a514a56191adef75b9f305","tid":2267604,"uid":210755,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:48:30.000Z","msg":"小朋友識唔識尊重就係要佢自己教, 但佢反而選擇發脾氣打 仲要掌摑,對小朋友嘅傷害仲大過肉體痛楚"},{"pid":"f9af100bcaae5f8912d9db659228eabf1ce4d155","tid":2267604,"uid":236891,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ce995a1f342bcbad067b5eb1b953e3592899444c","tid":2267604,"uid":219583,"like":181,"dislike":3,"score":178,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:55:05.000Z","msg":"成鳩日拎三級相同個仔出黎做新聞<br />\n收檔啦屌你老母<br />\n你個仔係學校比人笑撚到臉都